relevant_findings.general: No acute distress, laying in bed comfortably, speaking full sentences
relevant_findings.HEENT: Atraumatic/Nontender, Extraocular Movements Intact, Pupils Equal, Round, Reactive to Light, Anicteric sclera, Pink conjunctiva, Mucous membranes dry
relevant_findings.neck: Nontender, supple, no lymphadenopathy, no jugular venous distention
relevant_findings.cardiac: Mild tachycardia, S1/S2, no murmurs, gallops, or rubs
relevant_findings.lung: Clear to auscultation bilaterally, no wheezes, rales, rhonchi, breathing comfortably without use of accessory muscles
relevant_findings.abdomen: Distended, positive bowel sounds, nontender in all quadrants, no rebound or guarding
relevant_findings.extremities: 2+ edema above the ankles, no cyanosis, clubbing, warm and well perfused, no excoriations or lesions, no rashes
